{"id":4436,"date":"2018-04-20T15:49:03","date_gmt":"2018-04-20T19:49:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/charlie-rivard-grande-gagnante-du-concours-les-voix-de-la-poesie-edition-2018\/"},"modified":"2023-06-14T13:18:53","modified_gmt":"2023-06-14T17:18:53","slug":"charlie-rivard-grande-gagnante-du-concours-les-voix-de-la-poesie-edition-2018","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/charlie-rivard-grande-gagnante-du-concours-les-voix-de-la-poesie-edition-2018\/","title":{"rendered":"Charlie Rivard, grande gagnante du concours Les Voix de la po\u00e9sie, \u00e9dition 2018"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Hier soir, \u00e0 Toronto, Charlie Rivard, \u00e9tudiante de Litt\u00e9rature, a m\u00e9rit\u00e9 la premi\u00e8re place lors du concours Les Voix de la po\u00e9sie. Cet honneur s&rsquo;accompagne d&rsquo;une bourse de\u00a01000$ qui sera remise \u00e0 la biblioth\u00e8que du Coll\u00e8ge.<\/p>\n<p>Ce succ\u00e8s est sans contredit le fruit du travail et de l&rsquo;engagement de plusieurs personnes, Charlie Rivard, la premi\u00e8re, mais aussi d&rsquo;enseignantes et enseignants engag\u00e9s, qui ont cru en cette belle activit\u00e9 artistique et que nous remercions.<\/p>\n<p>Apr\u00e8s avoir brill\u00e9 au concours C\u00e9geps en spectacle l&rsquo;an dernier, Charlie a d\u00e9montr\u00e9 une fois de plus que la passion, le talent, la d\u00e9termination et l&rsquo;accompagnement professionnel m\u00e8nent tout droit au succ\u00e8s.<\/p>\n<p>Enfin, le Coll\u00e8ge tient \u00e0 f\u00e9liciter Charlie Rivard pour sa victoire et \u00e0 souligner l&rsquo;apport particulier de Maya Gobeil, enseignante et coordonnatrice du programme Th\u00e9\u00e2tre, qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 aux premi\u00e8res loges tout au long de la pr\u00e9paration de la participante au concours et des diff\u00e9rentes \u00e9tapes qui l&rsquo;ont men\u00e9e \u00e0 la victoire.<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>La Direction des communications<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hier soir, \u00e0 Toronto, Charlie Rivard, \u00e9tudiante de Th\u00e9\u00e2tre, a m\u00e9rit\u00e9 la premi\u00e8re place lors du concours Les Voix de la po\u00e9sie!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":4435,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[196],"etiquette-interne":[2301,2311,2321],"class_list":["post-4436","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle","sujet-actualite-honneurs","etiquette-interne-honneurs","etiquette-interne-theatre","etiquette-interne-litterature"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:17:04","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4436","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4436"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4436\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4834,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4436\/revisions\/4834"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4435"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4436"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=